data.description: Welcome to 619 S Rose Street! Nestled in the heart of Canton, this meticulously updated 2-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and city living. Immerse yourself in the vibrant neighborhood, as this residence is within walking distance to Patterson Park, Safeway, Canton Square, The Can Company shops, and more!  The main level exudes warmth with hardwood floors throughout. A spacious living area seamlessly connects to a separate dining room, creating an inviting space for both relaxation and entertaining. The updated kitchen is a culinary haven, featuring granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample cabinet space. Conveniently located towards the back of the main level is a half bath, offering ease and practicality.  Step through the sliding glass door to discover your private oasis—an inviting patio, a generously sized storage shed, and an elevated deck providing a perfect retreat.  Ascend to the top level, where wood floors lead you to the master suite. This sanctuary boasts a brand-new attached bath, two closets, and an abundance of natural light streaming through a large window overlooking the patio and the freshly built deck.  Don't miss the opportunity to make 619 S Rose Street your home, where modern amenities meet the charm of city living. Schedule your showing today and embrace the vibrant lifestyle that awaits in this Canton gem!
